---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Community Posting
metaDescription: Send community-serving White Plains information to WPCNA for review.
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Share with your neighbors</p>
    <h1>Community Posting</h1>
    <p>Have something useful for White Plains residents? Send it to WPCNA for review.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap posting-page">
    <section class="posting-intro" aria-labelledby="posting-resource-heading">
      <h2 id="posting-resource-heading">A curated community resource</h2>
      <p>This page is for local information that serves White Plains residents and neighborhoods.</p>
      <p>WPCNA reviews submissions before anything is posted. The goal is to share useful civic, neighborhood, and community updates &mdash; not classifieds, advertising, or personal listings.</p>
      <p>Submitting an item does not guarantee it will be posted. If it fits WPCNA&rsquo;s guidelines, it may be shared on the site, circulated through the council, or used to help residents stay informed.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="card-grid card-grid-2 posting-grid">
      <article class="resource-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">What&rsquo;s welcome</p>
        <h3>Community-serving information</h3>
        <ul class="plain-list">
          <li>Neighborhood events, school picnics, cleanups, and local meetings</li>
          <li>Civic or educational efforts, including awareness campaigns and newsletters</li>
          <li>City-related notices such as hydrant flushing, road work, or public-interest updates</li>
          <li>Local initiatives that help residents stay informed or get involved</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="resource-card">
        <p class="eyebrow">What we don&rsquo;t post</p>
        <h3>Not classifieds or advertising</h3>
        <ul class="plain-list">
          <li>Yard sales, personal listings, or private services</li>
          <li>Business advertising, promotions, or commercial offers</li>
          <li>Unreviewed announcements or anything that must appear immediately</li>
          <li>Items unrelated to White Plains residents or neighborhood life</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="posting-include" aria-labelledby="posting-include-heading">
      <h2 id="posting-include-heading">What to include</h2>
      <p>Please include the basics residents will need: what you are sharing, who it is for, when it happens, where it takes place, and any link WPCNA should use if the item is posted.</p>
      <p>Keep your message brief and clear. If WPCNA needs more information, someone may follow up.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="sidebar-card posting-form-card" id="posting-form" aria-labelledby="posting-form-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Submission form</p>
      <h2 id="posting-form-heading">Send something for review</h2>
      <p>Use this form to send community information to WPCNA. Submissions are reviewed before posting.</p>
      <p class="form-note">Your email address is used for follow-up and will not be published unless you specifically ask WPCNA to include it.</p>

      <form class="contact-form" data-posting-form data-posting-api="{{ site.postingApiUrl }}">
        {# Honeypot hidden from real users; catches automated submissions. #}
        <div class="form-honeypot" hidden aria-hidden="true">
          <label for="posting-website">Leave blank</label>
          <input id="posting-website" name="website" type="text" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off">
        </div>

        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="posting-name">Name</label>
          <input id="posting-name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="posting-email">Email</label>
          <input id="posting-email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="posting-subject">Subject</label>
          <input id="posting-subject" name="subject" type="text" maxlength="200" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="posting-message">Message <span class="char-hint" data-char-count>240 characters</span></label>
          <textarea id="posting-message" name="message" rows="5" maxlength="240" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" type="submit" data-posting-submit>Send for review</button>
        <p class="form-note">Submitting an item does not guarantee posting.</p>

        <div class="form-status" data-posting-status hidden></div>
      </form>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>
